data.description: Welcome to this well maintained 3 bedroom, 2 full bath home in The Timbers 2 Addition.  This beauty offers a split floorplan, roomy primary suite with wood flooring, carpeted secondary bedrooms are just as spacious, gas log fireplace, crown molding in living/dining area, granite countertops in kitchen, double pantry in laundry, privacy fence in back, oversized back patio (partially covered), 8 person stand alone storm shelter in garage. New HVAC and newer heavy composition roof.  Schedule your showing today to see all this home has to offer. *Seller offering $1,000 carpet allowance*
